\c 13
\s Ukuzalwa kukaSamsoni
\p
\v 1 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli babuya-ke benza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 2.11. 3.7. 4.1. 6.1. 10.6.\x*\nd*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasibanikela esandleni samaFilisti iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 3.31. 10.7. 1 Sam. 12.9.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Kwakukhona-ke umuntu othile weZora, owosendo lwakoDani, obizo lakhe lalinguManowa\x + Josh. 15.33.\x*; lomkakhe wayeyinyumba engazali\x + 1 Sam. 1.2. Luka 1.7.\x*.
\v 3 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasibonakala kowesifazana yathi kuye: Khangela-ke, uyinyumba, kawuzali, kodwa uzathatha isisu uzale indodana\x + 6.12. Luka 1.11,13.\x*.
\v 4 Ngakho-ke ake uqaphelise, unganathi wayini lokunathwayo okulamandla, ungadli lalutho olungcolileyo\x + 13.7,14. Nani 6.2,3. Luka 1.15.\x*,
\v 5 ngoba khangela, uzathatha isisu uzale indodana. Impuco kayiyikudlula\f + \fk kayiyikudlula: \fl Heb. \fq kayiyikwenyukela.\f* ekhanda layo\x + 16.17. 1 Sam. 1.11. Nani 6.5.\x*, ngoba umfana uzakuba ngumNaziri kaNkulunkulu kusukela esizalweni\x + Nani 6.2.\x*; yena uzaqala ukusindisa uIsrayeli esandleni samaFilisti\x + 1 Sam. 7.13. 2 Sam. 8.1. 1 Lan. 18.1.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Owesifazana wasesiza wabikela indoda yakhe esithi: Kufikile kimi umuntu kaNkulunkulu\x + Dute. 33.1. 1 Sam. 2.27. 9.6,7. 1 Kho. 13.1. 17.24. 2 Kho. 23.17.\x*, ukubonakala kwakhe kwakunjengokubonakala kwengilosi kaNkulunkulu, kusesabeka kakhulu\x + Dan. 10.5,6. Mat. 28.3. Seb. 6.15.\x*; kodwa kangimbuzanga\x + Gen. 16.8.\x* ukuthi uvela ngaphi\x + Gen. 16.8.\x*, futhi kangitshelanga ibizo lakhe\x + 13.17,18.\x*.
\v 7 Kodwa uthe kimi: Khangela, uzathatha isisu, uzale indodana; khathesi-ke unganathi wayini lokunathwayo okulamandla, ungadli lalutho olungcolileyo, ngoba umfana uzakuba ngumNaziri kaNkulunkulu kusukela esizalweni kuze kube sosukwini lokufa kwakhe\x + 13.3-5.\x*.
\p
\v 8 UManowa waseyincenga iN\nd kosi\nd* wathi: Hawu Nkosi yami, umuntu kaNkulunkulu omthumileyo ake abuye futhi kithi, asifundise ukuthi sizakwenza njani emfaneni ozazalwa.
\v 9 UNkulunkulu waselizwa ilizwi likaManowa, lengilosi kaNkulunkulu yafika futhi kowesifazana ehlezi egangeni; kodwa uManowa umkakhe wayengelaye.
\v 10 Owesifazana wasehaluzela wagijima wabikela umkakhe wathi: Khangela, lowomuntu ubonakele kimi owafika kimi mhla\add lokhuyana\add*.
\v 11 UManowa wasesukuma walandela umkakhe, wafika kulowomuntu wathi kuye: Unguye yini lowomuntu owakhuluma kulowesifazana? Wasesithi: Ngi\add nguye\add*.
\v 12 UManowa wasesithi: Kaweze-ke amazwi akho; izakuba yini indlela yomfana, lomsebenzi wakhe?
\v 13 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuManowa: Kukho konke engakutshoyo kowesifazana akuqaphelise;
\v 14 angadli okolutho oluphuma evinini lewayini, anganathi wayini lokunathwayo okulamandla, angadli lutho olungcolileyo; konke engamlaya khona akugcine\x + 13.4.\x*.
\p
\v 15 UManowa wasesithi engilosini yeN\nd kosi\nd*: Ake sikubambelele, silungise phambi kwakho izinyane lembuzi.
\v 16 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuManowa: Uba ungibambelela, kangiyikudla okwesinkwa sakho; njalo uba ulungisa umnikelo wokutshiswa, unikele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni. Ngoba uManowa wayengazi ukuthi yayiyingilosi yeN\nd kosi\x + 6.18. Gen. 18.5.\x*\nd*.
\v 17 UManowa wasesithi kuyo ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd*: Ungubani ibizo lakho, ukuze kuthi lapho amazwi akho esiza sikuhloniphe\x + 13.6.\x*.
\v 18 Ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuye: Ubuzelani kanje ngebizo lami lokhu liyamangalisa\x + Gen. 32.29.\x*?
\v 19 UManowa wasethatha izinyane lembuzi\x + 6.19,20.\x* lomnikelo wokudla, wakunikela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni phezu kwedwala, yasisenza ngokumangalisayo, njalo uManowa lomkakhe bekhangele\x + 6.18.\x*.
\v 20 Kwasekusithi lapho ilangabi lisenyuka elathini liqonde emazulwini, ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* yenyuka ngelangabi lelathi\x + 6.21.\x*, uManowa lomkakhe bekhangele, bathi mbo ngobuso babo emhlabathini\x + 1 Lan. 21.16. Hez. 1.28. Mat. 17.6. Levi 9.24.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd* kayiphindanga isabonakala kuManowa lomkakhe. Khona uManowa wazi ukuthi kwakuyingilosi yeN\nd kosi\x + 6.22.\x*\nd*.
\v 22 UManowa wasesithi kumkakhe: Sizakufa lokufa ngoba sibone uNkulunkulu\x + 6.22. Gen. 32.30. Eks. 33.20. Dute. 5.26.\x*.
\v 23 Kodwa umkakhe wathi kuye: Uba iN\nd kosi\nd* ibithanda ukusibulala, ibingayikwemukela esandleni sethu umnikelo wokutshiswa lomnikelo wokudla, njalo ibingayikusitshengisa zonke lezizinto, njalo ibingayikusizwisa ngalesisikhathi \add izinto\add* ezinjengalezi\x + 13.16,19.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Owesifazana wasebeletha indodana, wayitha ibizo layo \add wathi\add* nguSamsoni\x + Heb. 11.32.\x*; umfana wasekhula, leN\nd kosi\nd* yambusisa\x + 1 Sam. 2.21. 3.19. Luka 1.80. Luka 2.52.\x*.
\v 25 UMoya weN\nd kosi\nd* waseqala\x + 3.10.\x* ukumvusa enkambeni kaDani\x + Gen. 41.8.\x* phakathi kweZora leEshitawoli\x + Josh. 15.33.\x*.
